---
interface Props {
  title: string;
}
const { title } = Astro.props;
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="AI, 누구나 쓸 수 있습니다 - AI 도구 추천, 강좌, 지원사업, 뉴스" />
  <link rel="sitemap" href="/sitemap-index.xml" />
  <title>{title} | AI코리아24</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-900 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
  <header class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50">
    <nav class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">AI코리아24</a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-primary">블로그</a>
        <a href="/tools" class="hover:text-primary">AI 도구</a>
        <a href="/courses" class="hover:text-primary">AI 강좌</a>
        <a href="/grants" class="hover:text-primary">지원사업</a>
        <a href="/news" class="hover:text-primary">AI 뉴스</a>
        <a href="/community" class="hover:text-primary">커뮤니티</a>
      </div>
      <a href="/login" class="bg-primary text-white text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">로그인</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-1 pb-16 md:pb-0">
    <slot />
  </main>

  <footer class="hidden md:block bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm">AI코리아24 | AI, 누구나 쓸 수 있습니다</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">AI 도구, 강좌, 지원사업, 뉴스를 한국어로 큐레이션하는 서비스입니다. 본 사이트에서 제공하는 정보는 참고용이며, 정확한 내용은 해당 기관에서 확인하시기 바랍니다. 오류, 누락에 대하여 당사는 책임지지 않으며 그 결과에 대해 법적인 책임을 지지 않습니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-4">
        스타일 팩토리9 | 대표: 조진연 | 사업자등록번호: 672-43-00632 | 경기도 의정부시 호암로 256, 107-1804 (우 11638)<br />
        jinyeon_cho@hotmail.com
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 text-xs text-gray-500">
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-primary">회사소개</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-primary font-bold">개인정보처리방침</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-primary">이용약관</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-primary">문의</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <nav class="md:hidden fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white border-t border-gray-200 z-50">
    <div class="flex justify-around py-2">
      <a href="/" class="flex flex-col items-center text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-primary">
        <span class="text-lg">🏠</span>홈
      </a>
      <a href="/tools" class="flex flex-col items-center text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-primary">
        <span class="text-lg">🛠️</span>도구
      </a>
      <a href="/blog" class="flex flex-col items-center text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-primary">
        <span class="text-lg">📝</span>블로그
      </a>
      <a href="/community" class="flex flex-col items-center text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-primary">
        <span class="text-lg">💬</span>커뮤니티
      </a>
      <a href="/about" class="flex flex-col items-center text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-primary">
        <span class="text-lg">ℹ️</span>더보기
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</body>
</html>
<style is:global>
  @import '../styles/global.css';
</style>
